\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {5}{\ignorespaces Treatment effects on trust in climate scientists (multidimensional scale). Interventions are ordered by effect size (largest to smallest). The estimate column reports OLS coefficients with HC2 robust standard errors; significance stars are based on BH-adjusted p-values across all 20 intervention-vs-control comparisons. Both unadjusted and BH-adjusted p-values are reported. 95\% confidence intervals are not adjusted for multiple comparisons. In this preregistration, data are simulated at random, thus we should not expect to see any significant effects.}}{61}{table.caption.46}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{tbl-main-models}{{5}{61}{Treatment effects on trust in climate scientists (multidimensional scale). Interventions are ordered by effect size (largest to smallest). The estimate column reports OLS coefficients with HC2 robust standard errors; significance stars are based on BH-adjusted p-values across all 20 intervention-vs-control comparisons. Both unadjusted and BH-adjusted p-values are reported. 95\% confidence intervals are not adjusted for multiple comparisons. In this preregistration, data are simulated at random, thus we should not expect to see any significant effects}{table.caption.46}{}}
